' @id(DOM-AGENT-PREP)
' @desc(DOM-AGENT-PREP, "The mdd-agent crate's domain (crates/mdd-agent/src/lib.rs): AgentKind (Cursor | Codex | Claude | Generic) with parse() from a string and per-kind file_stem/label; prepare_agent(project, kind) producing an AgentPreparationReport { instruction_file: String, hooks_run: Vec<String> }. write_agent_instructions writes .mdd/docs/<stem>-mdd.md; run_pre_code_hooks discovers and runs .mdd/hooks/pre-code* in sorted order (fail-fast). As of cycle 0020 these types are mapped and reachable through the CMP-AGENT-PREPARE CLI caller.")
title MDD agent preparation — domain (current)

class AgentKind <<enum>> <<added>> {
  Cursor
  Codex
  Claude
  Generic
  +parse(value): AgentKind
}

class AgentPreparationReport {
  +instruction_file: String
  +hooks_run: Vec<String>
}

AgentKind --> AgentPreparationReport : prepare_agent() produces

note bottom of AgentPreparationReport
  prepare_agent writes .mdd/docs/<agent>-mdd.md and runs
  .mdd/hooks/pre-code* (sorted, fail-fast). Reported back to
  the CLI for stdout.
end note
